1
00:00:06,087 --> 00:00:10,583
We should concern ourselves with those,
whose opinion matters.

2
00:00:10,583 --> 00:00:14,076
[Vox Populi is not Vox Dei]

3
00:00:14,356 --> 00:00:19,416
They assert this

4
00:00:21,996 --> 00:00:26,124
with implication that,

5
00:00:26,124 --> 00:00:31,794
“Don’t concern yourself with things divine
that you can’t verify.”

6
00:00:31,794 --> 00:00:34,688
Like, in the times of the Greeks, 
when they’re talking about,

7
00:00:34,688 --> 00:00:37,495
“Are you pleasing
the gods or not?”

8
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:39,995
I can say, “Come on, 
you don’t know. 
 

9
00:00:39,995 --> 00:00:41,619
How you are going 
to know that?

10
00:00:41,619 --> 00:00:45,092
Have you seen any gods
or goddesses recently?

11
00:00:46,042 --> 00:00:52,456
So, forget that. You can see me, 
I can see you.

12
00:00:52,456 --> 00:00:56,590
We matter, 
our opinions matter.”

13
00:00:56,590 --> 00:01:00,180
Vox populi is vox Dei

14
00:01:00,450 --> 00:01:05,157
This is an indirect way 
of saying that,

15
00:01:05,157 --> 00:01:12,574
to exalt the opinions of man
over that of God.

16
00:01:12,574 --> 00:01:16,244
Flaw of secular humanism.

17
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:18,890
Suicidal move.

18
00:01:18,890 --> 00:01:22,580
What Alexander Solzhenitsyn called

19
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:28,650
‘the disastrous deviation
of the Enlightenment’.

20
00:01:30,290 --> 00:01:34,135
Ironically called “Enlightenment”.

21
00:01:34,155 --> 00:01:40,461
A movement that eliminates 
God as a factor

22
00:01:40,461 --> 00:01:43,402
is called “Enlightenment”.

23
00:01:44,182 --> 00:01:51,984
So they say that irony
is the driving force in literature.

24
00:01:51,984 --> 00:01:55,615
So what could be 
more ironic than that?

25
00:01:56,487 --> 00:01:59,743
kāma—andha-tamaḥ
 [CC: 1.4.171]

26
00:01:59,743 --> 00:02:02,019
“Dense darkness”—to say,

27
00:02:02,019 --> 00:02:06,684
to remove the God-concept is 
“Enlightenment thinkers”.

28
00:02:06,684 --> 00:02:07,454
[Laughing]

29
00:02:07,544 --> 00:02:11,665
Vox populi is not vox Dei.

30
00:02:11,788 --> 00:02:15,453
The sum total of the finite is never 
equal to the Infinite.

